A majestic, imposing angelic figure stands tall, with outstretched wings forming sharp, geometric triangle shapes, shimmering in brilliant white light; below her, various abstract triangular creatures fill the scene, each with edges and angles inspired by scalene, isoceles, and equilateral triangles, representing different abilities; the style is striking and literal, focusing on the mathematical and geometric motifs, with a sense of divine aura and radiant hope.